{"tid":1925700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本豪捐1.5億美元給WHO   譚德塞大讚安倍「抗疫有方」","createTime":"2020-03-14T14:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T20:53:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":257,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"8bcd54bb8b4462b08583a577d1b8c018cc9b9e1d","tid":1925700,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"日本共同社報導，世界衛生組織秘書長譚德塞13日在記者會提及日本首相安倍晉三，稱讚他領導抗疫有方。報導指出，譚德塞在記者會特別提及國家領導人並稱讚的舉動相當罕見。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞稱讚日本因應新冠肺炎疫情的措施及安倍領導下的政府調度，並提到日本捐給世衛1億5500萬美元（約台幣46億6600萬元）。此前譚德塞曾多次提及中國大陸國家主席習近平積極抗疫，並感謝中國捐款2000萬美元（約台幣6億元）。<br />\n<br />\n日本外交界人士私下表示，「簡直是毫不避諱的口惠」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4414809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F4414809&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=784ab962\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4414809</a>"},{"pid":"3ca905767ad8f3de9b4d4e92b77181e782530849","tid":1925700,"uid":189328,"like":192,"dislike":1,"score":191,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"有錢的話意大利都可以表揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96298f218ba8fea9dc0a397a980de54f1d12bb01","tid":1925700,"uid":80651,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"東京奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63dfac3ad9230c33e4e5702e3db9b30ee61e6e4","tid":1925700,"uid":7828,"like":249,"dislike":1,"score":248,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4HBZ1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4HBZ1D.jpg&h=d37be882&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99c81271f8c7386916bd145e3586acf1e5e32165","tid":1925700,"uid":227271,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"國際級代言人，收錢就會幫你講說話<img 